channel.title: I am once again asking for a collaboration. - CLOME [Collab?]
channel.description:
Hey guys! I hope this post finds you doing well. I’ve hit a producer’s block recently, and I was wondering if a collaboration may help me out! It can be any genre or vibe, although I’d like to say that I specialize in trap or that spectrum of electronic music. If you would like to listen to some of my tracks, you can find them at soundcloud.com/clomemusic I also have some WIPs that could work as a stepping stone, but I have no preferences. Have a great day! CLOME
Here are some demos: https://app.auxy.co/projects/KQQ3pdKXkspOBHSMuclHmA== https://app.auxy.co/projects/npPTrIJl-Ls399kskkmTKw== https://app.auxy.co/projects/uWmcDGlpdDiBq3PsG8CHjA==
